subject: United States Open (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: Through three rounds, Beau Hossler has shown he isn’t ready to go away. He finished Saturday tied for eighth, one stroke ahead of Tiger Woods, and now believes he can win at the Olympic Club.
